- Monks~
@73   = ~The mace is a direct descendant of the basic club, being nothing more than a wooden shaft with a stone or iron head mounted on the end. The head design varies; some being spiked, others flanged, and still others have pyramidal knobs. 

The dwarven smith Breagar has improved this weapon, so it won't break during a fight.

STATISTICS:

Damage: 1d6 +1 (Crushing)
Weight: 10
Speed Factor: 7
Requirement: 10 Strength
Proficiency Type: Mace
