- Druids
- Mages
- Monks~
@75   = ~The typical dagger has a pointed, usually double-edged blade, as opposed to a knife, which has a single edge and is a bit shorter than the dagger. 

The dwarven smith Breagar has improved this weapon, so it won't break during a fight.

STATISTICS:

Damage: 1d4 (Piercing)
Weight: 1
Speed Factor: 2
Proficiency Type: Dagger
Type: 1-handed

Not usable by:
