@83   = ~The wakizashi, or companion sword is extremely important to samurai. It is worn at all times, even indoors, and is near the samurai when he sleeps at night. As finely made as the katana, the wakizashi, a shorter sword with a length between 12 and 24 inches, is a dangerous weapon in the hands of a skilled user.

The dwarven smith Breagar has improved this weapon, so it won't break during a fight.

