@10065 = ~The Tower of Anstinus is under siege

Breagar was satisfied that we cleared out the drow from the basement of the tower. Now we have to take care of the upper levels.~

/* Forres and Reggik */
@10066 = ~The Tower of Anstinus is under siege

We faced drow and beholders in the basement and the duergar dwelling, but we were able to defeat them. With Berronar's divine support, Breagar sealed the underground entrance of the tower, to protect the duergar from future drow attacks. Now all that is left to do, is to inform Reggik and Forres.~

/* Forres and Graschek */
@10067 = ~The Tower of Anstinus is under siege

We faced drow and beholders in the basement and the duergar dwelling, but we were able to defeat them. With Berronar's divine support, Breagar sealed the underground entrance of the tower, to protect the duergar from future drow attacks. Now all that is left to do, is to inform Graschek and Forres.~

